# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) for local development, or set in CI.
#
# OpenRouter API key — baked into the bundle at `vite build` time so that
# end users (teachers) don't have to enter one. If left empty, the UI will
# prompt for a key and store it in localStorage instead.
#
# Get a free key at https://openrouter.ai/keys
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
